  "title": "Mechanical & Electrical Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>M &amp; E Engineer</strong></p>\n<p>(Building Construction/Project)</p>\n<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Site planning, inspections and coordination with consultants, subcontractors &amp; clients on M&amp;E requirements and specifications</li>\n  <li>Prepare and create detail work schedule, manpower and resource planning</li>\n  <li>Coordinate for submission documents, and approval, all shop drawings, samples, coordination drawings and supervision</li>\n  <li>Coordinate the safety management; system on site</li>\n  <li>Follow up and reporting on the project progress</li>\n  <li>Plan, monitor and ensure work-in-progress at site are on schedule</li>\n  <li>Prepare and compile as built drawings for submission</li>\n  <li>Identify discrepancies, assess, and recommend M&amp;E Subcontractors’ claims</li>\n  <li>Any other ad hoc duties as assigned by the Management or your Superior</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Recognized Degree in Mechanical &amp; Electrical Engineering or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Well versed in AutoCAD</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of BIM would be an added advantage</li>\n  <li>Minimum 5 years construction trade experience preferably in non residential projects, completed at least one project cycle</li>\n  <li>Preferred Singaporean to apply</li>\n</ul>",
